---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Tutors & Music Teachers — Student Testimonials That Fill Your Calendar | SocialProof" description="Tutors, music teachers, and instructors: collect parent and student testimonials automatically. SocialProof builds the trust that books more lessons and fills your schedule.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Tutors & Instructors
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Parents searching for a tutor or music teacher want certainty. They're spending real money on their child's development, and they can't afford to guess. SocialProof helps tutors, music teachers, language instructors, and coaches collect student and parent testimonials — and display them where decisions get made.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why testimonials matter more when kids are involved</h2>
      <p>When a parent is evaluating a tutor, they're not just comparing qualifications — they're evaluating fit, safety, and results. "My daughter went from failing algebra to a B+" is infinitely more powerful than any credential. Real testimonials from real parents answer the questions a qualifications list never can.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">SocialProof gives you a simple way to collect those stories from satisfied families and display them where prospective parents will see them.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What converts parents and students</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Academic results:</strong> "Grade went from C to A- in one semester. First time he's actually looked forward to studying."</li>
        <li><strong>Teaching approach:</strong> "Explains things in multiple ways until it clicks. Incredibly patient."</li>
        <li><strong>Music progress:</strong> "Playing her first full song in 3 months. She practices without being asked now."</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> "Updates us after every session. We always know exactly how our son is progressing."</li>
        <li><strong>Confidence building:</strong> "She didn't just improve her math — she stopped believing she was 'bad at math.'"</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for instructors</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your website or tutoring profile page — quick setup, no tech skills needed.</li>
        <li><strong>After a milestone</strong> (test passed, recital, end of semester), send the collection link to parents or adult students.</li>
        <li><strong>They submit feedback in 2 minutes</strong> — no account required.</li>
        <li><strong>You approve and publish</strong> — the testimonial appears on your site instantly.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every type of instruction</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Academic tutoring (math, science, English, SAT/ACT)</li>
        <li>Music lessons (piano, guitar, voice, violin)</li>
        <li>Language tutoring (ESL, Spanish, Mandarin)</li>
        <li>Test prep and college admissions coaching</li>
        <li>Learning differences & special needs tutoring</li>
        <li>Online / virtual instruction</li>
        <li>Art, drama, and creative skills instruction</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#eff6ff;border:1px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#1d4ed8;">
          "I have 14 parent testimonials on my tutoring page now. New inquiries almost always mention them. It's basically word-of-mouth, but it works even when nobody personally referred them."
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#1e3a8a;">— Independent math tutor, high school & SAT prep</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start free</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for 1 active widget. Perfect for solo instructors building their reputation. Paid plans available as your practice grows.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <a href="/signup" style="display:inline-block;background:#2563eb;color:white;padding:0.85rem 2.2rem;border-radius:8px;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">
          Start collecting testimonials free
        </a>
        <p style="margin-top:0.75rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#888;">Free forever for 1 active widget. No credit card.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
